MatrixEmu - an emulation of the scrolling console text in 'the Matrix'

Dependencies
* ncurses C library
* pthread C++11 library

Install -- installs to ~/bin by default, change it or add it to your PATH
$ git clone https://github.com/dburggie/matrixemu.git
$ cd matrixemu
$ make all
$ make install




Features
* multiply simultaneous descending columns
* columns descend with independent speeds
* columns have independent lengths
* columns fade evenly to black from their head to their tail


